    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Trim the green stalk[s] off your <strong>aubergine[s]</strong> and chop into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped aubergine</strong> to a large baking tray (or two!)</p>",
