      "instruction": "<p>Give everything a really good mix up and put the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span>in the oven for an initial 20 min – these are your <strong>Mediterranean-style vegetables</strong></p><p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>red wine vinegar</strong>, with your <strong>Dijon mustard </strong>(not a mustard fan? Go easy!)<strong> </strong>and<strong> </strong>2 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [3 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> in a small bowl – this is your <strong>vinaigrette</strong></p>",
