    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the Mediterranean-style vegetables have been roasting for 20 min, remove the tray[s]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>from the oven and tear your<strong> ciabatta[s]</strong> into large pieces over the top and drizzle the torn bread with a little <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for 6-7 min further or until the bread is lightly golden and starting to crisp, then sprinkle over your <strong>pine nut & seed mix</strong> and return to the oven for a final 3-4 min or until toasted and lightly golden</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don't burn!</p>",
