    {
      "instruction": "<p>Carefully squeeze the <strong>roasted</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> out of the skin and discard the skin</p><p>To serve, top the <strong>salad </strong>with the <strong>Mediterranean-style vegetables</strong>, <strong>crispy bread</strong>, <strong>roasted garlic</strong> and<strong> toasted pine nuts & seeds </strong>– this is your <strong>Mediterranean-style vegetable panzanella</strong></p><p>Tear your <strong>basil leaves </strong>all over, drizzle over the <strong>vinaigrette</strong>, season with a grind of <strong>black</strong> <strong>pepper</strong> and dig in!</p>",
